com.scvngr.levelup.core.annotation

Annotation Type AccessTokenRequired


  • @Documented
@Retention(value=CLASS)
public @interface AccessTokenRequired
    Denotes a LevelUp web request that requires an AccessToken. Callers should ensure that they pass a non-null AccessTokenRetriever to the Request factory that is creating the AbstractRequest.
